12#ifndef MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_CODECS_VP9_LIBVPX_VP9_DECODER_H_
13#define MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_CODECS_VP9_LIBVPX_VP9_DECODER_H_
14
15#ifdef RTC_ENABLE_VP9
16
17#include "api/transport/webrtc_key_value_config.h"
18#include "api/video_codecs/video_decoder.h"
19#include "common_video/include/video_frame_buffer_pool.h"
20#include "modules/video_coding/codecs/vp9/include/vp9.h"
21#include "modules/video_coding/codecs/vp9/vp9_frame_buffer_pool.h"
22#include "vpx/vp8cx.h"
23
24namespace webrtc {
25
26class LibvpxVp9Decoder : public VP9Decoder {
27 public:
28 LibvpxVp9Decoder();
29 explicit LibvpxVp9Decoder(const WebRtcKeyValueConfig& trials);
30
31 virtual ~LibvpxVp9Decoder();
32
33 int InitDecode(const VideoCodec* inst, int number_of_cores) override;
34
35 int Decode(const EncodedImage& input_image,
36 bool missing_frames,
37 int64_t /*render_time_ms*/) override;
38
39 int RegisterDecodeCompleteCallback(DecodedImageCallback* callback) override;
40
41 int Release() override;
42
43 DecoderInfo GetDecoderInfo() const override;
44 const char* ImplementationName() const override;
45
46 private:
47 int ReturnFrame(const vpx_image_t* img,
48 uint32_t timestamp,
49 int qp,
50 const webrtc::ColorSpace* explicit_color_space);
51
52 // Memory pool used to share buffers between libvpx and webrtc.
53 Vp9FrameBufferPool libvpx_buffer_pool_;
54 // Buffer pool used to allocate additionally needed NV12 buffers.
55 VideoFrameBufferPool output_buffer_pool_;
56 DecodedImageCallback* decode_complete_callback_;
57 bool inited_;
58 vpx_codec_ctx_t* decoder_;
59 bool key_frame_required_;
60 VideoCodec current_codec_;
61 int num_cores_;
62
63 // Decoder should produce this format if possible.
64 const VideoFrameBuffer::Type preferred_output_format_;
65};
66} // namespace webrtc
67
68#endif // RTC_ENABLE_VP9
69
70#endif // MODULES_VIDEO_CODING_CODECS_VP9_LIBVPX_VP9_DECODER_H_
